title: That Council approve the recommendation outlined in Report CAOPC23-009, dated November 22, 2023 of the Chief Administrative Officer as follows. That the Minutes of Settlement between the City and the Amalgamated Transit Union 1320 dated November 17, 2023 that sets out new terms for a Collective Agreement covering the three-year period July 1, 2023 to June 30, 2026, be approved.
23-111 - Being a By-law to confirm the proceedings of the Council at its meeting held on November 22, 2023.
That this meeting be adjourned at 5:54 p.m.
